channel.title: 508 help. Shouldn't be hard take a look
channel.description:
I always thought I would stick with 317s, but they're way behind runescape, and I figure people are moving away from 317s. So I've decided to create a 508. basically I downloaded the 508 cache from stormcutters tutorial(which I found very helpful) and extracted it into a folder I created called cache508 in the location run>C:
in return... when I run the server(tonypker13's rubikscape)
I get this: [img]http://i43.tinypic.com/v8k674.jpg[/img]
help would be very appreciated.
If you helped me and 508s started working for me, I would try my best to do something for you such as code a BufferWriter for your not-working ipban or maybe code a command/quest w/e for new coders.
Thank you.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 22, 2009, 07:58:22 pm[/size][hr]my email is dragongegsbob@gmail.com
